cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically improving visual place recognition using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization of the neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning, specifically reinforcement learning and optimization (cs.RO). The paper also involves experimentation and analysis of the results, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, specifically deep learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
